#### 3.2.1 Performance

**REQ-{{REQ_ID_PREFIX}}-NF-001** — Response time

| Field               | Value                                                         |
|---------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Statement           | The system shall respond to 95% of API requests within 200 ms under a load of [N] concurrent users. |
