| Verification method | Load test (tool: [k6 / Locust / JMeter])                     |
| Status              | Draft                                                         |

#### 3.2.2 Reliability

**REQ-{{REQ_ID_PREFIX}}-NF-002** — Availability

| Field               | Value                                                         |
|---------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Statement           | The system shall maintain an uptime of ≥99.5% measured monthly, excluding planned maintenance windows. |
| Priority            | Must                                                          |
| Verification method | Monitoring dashboard (tool: [Uptime Kuma / Cloudflare])       |
| Status              | Draft                                                         |

#### 3.2.3 Security

**REQ-{{REQ_ID_PREFIX}}-NF-003** — Authentication

| Field               | Value                                                         |
|---------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Statement           | All endpoints returning user data shall require a valid session token (JWT or equivalent). Unauthenticated requests shall receive HTTP 401. |
| Priority            | Must                                                          |
| Verification method | Automated security test (OWASP ZAP / manual penetration test) |
| Status              | Draft                                                         |

